msg: Improved patch for IBATISNET-100 to not throw a NullReferenceException if a cacheModel has a flushOnExecute node that references an invalid statement. A WARN message is issued instead (this may need to change to throwing a ConfigurationException). Thanks to Chad Humphries for discovering this.
